# Purpose:
# Write scripts governing cross layer alignment.
# Creates folder mytemp/cross_wkspc
#
# > cross_topscripts myxml -d=temp0 -zmin=i -zmax=j
#
# Options:
# -nf			;no foldmasks
# -abwide=5		;strip width in tiles
# -abscl=200	;size reduction factor
